.env.example

============================================
StockPredictionPro - .env.example
Copy this to ".env" and fill in the values
Do NOT commit your actual .env
============================================
App environment
ENVIRONMENT=development
APP_NAME=StockPredictionPro
APP_DEBUG=true

Timezone and locale
APP_TIMEZONE=UTC
APP_LOCALE=en_US

Data sources (primary + optional fallback)
Yahoo Finance is used via yfinance (no key needed).
Alpha Vantage is optional; add your free API key below.
ALPHA_VANTAGE_KEY=

Default market and tickers (used as UI presets; can be overridden in the app)
DEFAULT_MARKET=NSE
DEFAULT_TICKERS=INFY.NS,TCS.NS,RELIANCE.NS

Caching and storage (optional; enable only if wired)
USE_REDIS=false
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0

Database (optional; leave empty if not used)
DB_URL=

Logging and monitoring
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
SENTRY_DSN=

API service (optional Fast service layer)
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
API_ENABLE_CORS=true

Streamlit
STREAMLIT_SERVER_PORT=8501
STREAMLIT_HEADLESS=true
STREAMLIT_ENABLE_CORS=true
STREAMLIT_THEME=dark

Security (only for production setups)
JWT_SECRET=
JWT_ALGORITHM=HS256
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=*

Trading / backtest defaults (can be overridden in YAML configs or UI)
TX_COST_BPS=15
DEFAULT_PREDICTION_HORIZON=1

Governance (run metadata)
ENABLE_AUDIT_TRAILS=true
RUN_METADATA_AUTHOR=